OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome brightness to start then rain
OL,7,Fspreading north during the evening.
OL,8,FThis clearing shortly after midnight
OL,9,Fto leave a dry night with some clear
OL,10,Fspells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FWarm again. A quite cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning with patchy drizzle in the
OL,14,Fwest.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarm
OL,17,Fover the weekend and on Monday with
OL,18,Fsome bright or sunny spells, chance of
OL,19,Fsome rain later on Sunday.
